      "type": "p",
      "text": "Actions"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Claws. Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 4 (1d4 + 2) slashing damage."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Blinding Breath (Recharge 6). The mephit exhales a 15-- foot cone of blinding dust. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity saving throw or be blinded for 1 minute. A creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success."
    }
